{
    "poem_title": "À M. DAVID, STATUAIRE",
    "author": "Victor Hugo",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1831",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! que ne suis-je un de ces hommes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Qui, géants d'un siècle effacé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Jusque dans le siècle où nous sommes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Règnent du fond de leur passé !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Que ne suis-je, prince ou poète,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "De ces mortels à haute tête,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "D'un monde à la fois base et faîte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Que leur temps ne peut contenir ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Qui dans le calme ou dans l'orage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qu'on les adore ou les outrage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Devançant le pas de leur âge,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Marchent un pied dans l'avenir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oh ! que ne suis-je un de ces hommes\nQui, géants d'un siècle effacé,\nJusque dans le siècle où nous sommes\nRègnent du fond de leur passé !\nQue ne suis-je, prince ou poète,\nDe ces mortels à haute tête,\nD'un monde à la fois base et faîte,\nQue leur temps ne peut contenir ;\nQui dans le calme ou dans l'orage,\nQu'on les adore ou les outrage,\nDevançant le pas de leur âge,\nMarchent un pied dans l'avenir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Que ne suis-je une de ces flammes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Un de ces pôles glorieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Vers qui penchent toutes les âmes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sur qui se fixent tous les yeux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "De ces hommes dont les statues,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Du flot des temps toujours battues,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "D'un tel signe sont revêtues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Que, si le hasard les abat,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "S'il les détrône de leur sphère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Du bronze auguste on ne peut faire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Que des cloches pour la prière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Ou des canons pour le combat !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que ne suis-je une de ces flammes,\nUn de ces pôles glorieux,\nVers qui penchent toutes les âmes,\nSur qui se fixent tous les yeux !\nDe ces hommes dont les statues,\nDu flot des temps toujours battues,\nD'un tel signe sont revêtues\nQue, si le hasard les abat,\nS'il les détrône de leur sphère,\nDu bronze auguste on ne peut faire\nQue des cloches pour la prière\nOu des canons pour le combat !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Que n'ai-je un de ces fronts sublimes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "David ! Mon corps, fait pour souffrir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Du moins sous tes mains magnanimes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Renaîtrait pour ne plus mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Du haut du temple ou du théâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Colosse de bronze ou d'albâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Salué d'un peuple idolâtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Je surgirais sur la cité,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Comme un géant en sentinelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Couvrant la ville de mon aile,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Dans quelque attitude éternelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "De génie et de majesté !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que n'ai-je un de ces fronts sublimes,\nDavid ! Mon corps, fait pour souffrir,\nDu moins sous tes mains magnanimes\nRenaîtrait pour ne plus mourir !\nDu haut du temple ou du théâtre,\nColosse de bronze ou d'albâtre,\nSalué d'un peuple idolâtre,\nJe surgirais sur la cité,\nComme un géant en sentinelle,\nCouvrant la ville de mon aile,\nDans quelque attitude éternelle\nDe génie et de majesté !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Car c'est toi, lorsqu'un héros tombe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Qui le relèves souverain !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Toi qui le scelles sur sa tombe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il foule avec des pieds d'airain !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Rival de Rome et de Ferrare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Tu pétris pour le mortel rare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ou le marbre froid de Carrare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Ou le métal qui fume et bout.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Le grand homme au tombeau s'apaise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Quand ta main, à qui rien ne pèse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Hors du bloc ou de la fournaise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Le jette vivant et debout !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car c'est toi, lorsqu'un héros tombe,\nQui le relèves souverain !\nToi qui le scelles sur sa tombe\nQu'il foule avec des pieds d'airain !\nRival de Rome et de Ferrare,\nTu pétris pour le mortel rare\nOu le marbre froid de Carrare,\nOu le métal qui fume et bout.\nLe grand homme au tombeau s'apaise\nQuand ta main, à qui rien ne pèse,\nHors du bloc ou de la fournaise\nLe jette vivant et debout !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Sans toi peut-être sa mémoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Pâlirait d'un oubli fatal ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Mais c'est toi qui sculptes sa gloire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Visible sur un piédestal.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Ce fanal, perdu pour le monde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Feu rampant dans la nuit profonde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "S'éteindrait, sans montrer sur l'onde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Ni les écueils ni le chemin ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "C'est ton souffle qui le ranime ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "C'est toi qui, sur le sombre abîme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Dresses le colosse sublime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Qui prend le phare dans sa main.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sans toi peut-être sa mémoire\nPâlirait d'un oubli fatal ;\nMais c'est toi qui sculptes sa gloire\nVisible sur un piédestal.\nCe fanal, perdu pour le monde,\nFeu rampant dans la nuit profonde,\nS'éteindrait, sans montrer sur l'onde\nNi les écueils ni le chemin ;\nC'est ton souffle qui le ranime ;\nC'est toi qui, sur le sombre abîme,\nDresses le colosse sublime\nQui prend le phare dans sa main."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Lorsqu'à tes yeux une pensée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Sous les traits d'un grand homme a lui,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Tu la fais marbre, elle est fixée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Et les peuples disent : C'est lui !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Mais avant d'être pour la foule,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Longtemps dans ta tête elle roule",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Comme une flamboyante houle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Au fond du volcan souverain ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Loin du grand jour qui la réclame",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Tu la fais bouillir dans ton âme ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi de ses langues de flamme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Le feu saisit l'urne d'airain.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lorsqu'à tes yeux une pensée\nSous les traits d'un grand homme a lui,\nTu la fais marbre, elle est fixée,\nEt les peuples disent : C'est lui !\nMais avant d'être pour la foule,\nLongtemps dans ta tête elle roule\nComme une flamboyante houle\nAu fond du volcan souverain ;\nLoin du grand jour qui la réclame\nTu la fais bouillir dans ton âme ;\nAinsi de ses langues de flamme\nLe feu saisit l'urne d'airain."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Va ! que nos villes soient remplies",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "De tes colosses radieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Qu'à jamais tu te multiplies",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Dans un peuple de demi-dieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Fais de nos cités des Corinthes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! ta pensée a des étreintes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Dont l'airain garde les empreintes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Dont le granit s'enorgueillit !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Honneur au sol que ton pied foule !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Un métal dans tes veines coule ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Ta tête ardente est un grand moule",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "D'où l'idée en bronze jaillit !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Va ! que nos villes soient remplies\nDe tes colosses radieux !\nQu'à jamais tu te multiplies\nDans un peuple de demi-dieux !\nFais de nos cités des Corinthes !\nOh ! ta pensée a des étreintes\nDont l'airain garde les empreintes,\nDont le granit s'enorgueillit !\nHonneur au sol que ton pied foule !\nUn métal dans tes veines coule ;\nTa tête ardente est un grand moule\nD'où l'idée en bronze jaillit !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Bonaparte eût voulu renaître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "De marbre et géant sous ta main ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "Cromwell, son aïeul et son maître,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "T'eût livré son front surhumain ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 89,
                    "line_text": "Ton bras eût sculpté pour l'Espagne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 90,
                    "line_text": "Charles Quint ; pour nous, Charlemagne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 91,
                    "line_text": "Un pied sur l'hydre d'Allemagne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 92,
                    "line_text": "L'autre sur Rome aux sept coteaux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 93,
                    "line_text": "Au sépulcre prêt à descendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
